test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 2, 3, 999, 1000] == [1, 2]
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [1, 2]
  + [1, 2, 2, 3, 999, 1000]
test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 4, 2, 4] == [2, 4]
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 4
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4]
  + [2, 4, 4, 2, 4]
